here at the Library is

00:01:00.860 --> 00:01:05.900
that we are the chief steward of
the record of knowledge for America

00:01:05.900 --> 00:01:10.740
and world, thus creating a
springboard to the future.

00:01:10.740 --> 00:01:16.110
And the future I hope to see is one
of compassion and courage, industry

00:01:16.110 --> 00:01:22.190
and innovation, remarkable
accomplishment, achievement,

00:01:22.190 --> 00:01:24.840
