And tonight, we have an opportunity

00:01:54.680 --> 00:01:57.580
to enjoy a very special
creative endeavor

00:01:57.580 --> 00:02:00.270
with the spotlight
on native writers.

00:02:00.270 --> 00:02:04.190
This evening's event is sponsored
with the Library's Asian division

00:02:04.190 --> 00:02:07.070
and the Poetry and
Literature Center.

00:02:07.070 --> 00:02:12.030 position:56%
