launched in 1989.

00:02:35.720 --> 00:02:40.810
Manoa brings the literature of
Asia, the Pacific, and the Americas

00:02:40.810 --> 00:02:43.500
to English-speaking readers.

00:02:43.500 --> 00:02:46.720
To date, the journal has
published over 50 volumes

00:02:46.720 --> 00:02:53.140
of about 10,000 pages and over 1200
writers, translators, reviewers,

00:02:53.140 --> 00:02:56.680
and editors have participated
in those publications.

00:02:56.680 --> 00:03:00.510
To find out more-- yup.

00:03:00.510 --> 00:03:05.300
[ Applause ]

00:03:05.300 --> 00:03:10.120
To find out more about that
journal, please visit their website

00:03:10.120 --> 00:03:14.480
